Function Plots
==============

FIGURE My Plot  @fig:functions
    WIDTH=75
    CODE
        let f(x) = x^2
        let g(x) = 2x
        figure {
            x_axis(-5, 5, "x")  % x-min, y-max, label
            y_axis(-0.5, 4.5, "y")
            function(f)
            function(g)
            circle(0, 0, 0.1)   % x, y, radius
            circle(2, 4, 0.1)
        }
    CAPTION
        Some functions $f$ and $g$.
